{"tid":2410523,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕節、復活節、萬聖節等等的真相……人類仍然慶祝的Enkist節日","createTime":"2021-02-16T16:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T16:46:50.000Z","uid":364854,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc6ae388e425bdc5132c66f4b48fe2973c874f0","tid":2410523,"uid":364854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"西方傳統節日的習俗與我們形影不離︰聖誕節、復活節、萬聖節&hellip;&hellip;在近代才創立的節日，例如勞動節，亦是眾所周知。這些節日是普天同慶的良機，同時是Anu與蜥蜴人扭曲現實的鐵證。<strong><span class=\"red\">自4000年前以來，Anu與蜥蜴人操控地球，自此篡改一切歷史與神秘學知識，遠古人類曾慶祝的Enkist節日未能倖免︰</span></strong><br />\n&bull; Yule被篡改成聖誕節<br />\n&bull; Samhain被篡改成萬聖節<br />\n&bull; Ishtar被篡改成復活節<br />\n&bull; Beltane被貶低至勞動節<br />\n&bull; Imbolc成了「聖燭節」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n如今的世界是非顛倒，充斥着Anu與蜥蜴人編造的謊言。這個涵蓋宗教、政治、經濟、教育等等層面的龐大騙局，其目的只有一個︰奴役人類。惡人推廣的「節日」扭曲、矮化真相，同時讓部份真相和習俗留存，以便更易蒙騙人類。這席話令你驚愕？<strong>在物質主義的「狂歡」之中，請靜下心，認真研究各個節日的由來。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>《人類仍慶祝的Enkist節日》目錄</strong></span><br />\n第1章︰Samhain <br />\n<a href=\"https://enkishivasatyatruth.blogspot.com/2020/10/samhain-summary.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fenkishivasatyatruth.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F10%2Fsamhain-summary.html&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=c3373c63\" target=\"_blank\">https://enkishivasatyatruth.blogspot.com/2020/10/samhain-summary.html</a><br />\n第2章︰Yule<br />\n<a href=\"https://enkishivasatyatruth.blogspot.com/2020/12/Yule-and-more.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fenkishivasatyatruth.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F12%2FYule-and-more.html&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=0e54b8cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://enkishivasatyatruth.blogspot.com/2020/12/Yule-and-more.html</a><br />\n第3章︰Lammas和Summer Solstice<br />\n<a href=\"https://enkishivasatyatruth.blogspot.com/2021/02/lammas-and-summer-solstice.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fenkishivasatyatruth.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F0